; width: 480px;\">2、父母所在单位的营业执照复印件或者组织机构代码证复印件，需加盖公章。</p></dd></dl><dl class=\"dls\" style=\"width: 678px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; padding: 10px 2px 2px 35px; margin: 0px 0px 0px 6px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(153, 153, 153); color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; background: none rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span class=\"sp\">个人资产证明</span></dl><dl style=\"width: 678px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; padding: 12px 2px 10px 35px; margin: 3px 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; background-image: url(http://www.tigerwing.cn/Content/images/line_01.gif); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-position: 50% 100%; background-repeat: repeat-x;\"><dt style=\"width: 60px; float: left; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"vs_btn1\"><a href=\"http://www.tigerwing.cn/Visa/Visa/194?Keyword=%E4%B8%B9%E9%BA%A6#none\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; width: 65px; float: left; height: 23px; margin: 0px; cursor: default; background-image: url(http://www.tigerwing.cn/Content/images/visa_btn1.jpg); background-repeat: no-repeat;\"></a></span></dt><dt class=\"dtt\" style=\"width: 115px; float: left; margin: 0px;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(92, 92, 92); display: inline-block; margin: 0px; line-height: 14px;\">未成年人资金证明</strong></dt><dd style=\"width: 490px; float: left; margin-left: 10px; margin-top: -2px; vertical-align: middle;\"><p style=\"line-height: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 480px;\">请提供父母名下活期资金证明：</p><p style=\"line-height: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 480px;\">1、父母名下的工资卡银行对账单或工资存折原件，需有最近6个月记录，余额5万元或以上，近期不能有突然大笔金额存入，银行流水账单需有本人姓名以及加盖银行业务章；（该材料如有，必须提供）</p><p style=\"line-height: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 480p