height: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 480px;\">请提供覆盖整个行程有酒店网址链接的英文酒店确认单，必须是真实预订，并显示每一位入住人的姓名（与护照拼音一致）。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"dls list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"width: 678px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; padding: 10px 2px 2px 35px; margin: 0px 0px 0px 6px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(153, 153, 153); color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal; background: none rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span class=\"sp\">国际医疗保险</span></ul><ul style=\"width: 678px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; padding: 12px 2px 10px 35px; margin: 3px 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal; background-image: url(http://www.tigerwing.cn/Content/images/line_01.gif); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-position: 50% 100%; background-repeat: repeat-x;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p><span class=\"vs_btn2\"><a href=\"http://www.tigerwing.cn/Visa/Visa/160?Keyword=%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%A7%E5%88%A9#none\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; width: 65px; float: left; height: 23px; margin: 0px; cursor: default; background-image: url(http://www.tigerwing.cn/Content/images/visa_btn2.jpg); background-repeat: no-repeat;\"></a></span></p></li><li><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(92, 92, 92); display: inline-block; margin: 0px; line-height: 14px;\">国际医疗保险</strong></p></li><li><p style=\"line-height: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 480px;\">符合领馆要求的国际医疗保险：&nbsp;</p><p style=\"line-height: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 480px;\">1. 承保地区: • 申请申根签证，请购买申根国家区域适用的医疗保险 • 申请长期签证，请按照材料清单要求，如需保险，请购买适用的医疗保险&nbsp;</p><p style=\"line-height: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 480px;\">2. 须涵盖医疗保险和送返费用，医疗保险保额不低于3万欧元（约30万人民币）&nbsp;</p><p style=\"line-height: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 480px;\">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;须在覆盖在申根区的整个停留时间的基础上前后各加2天（例如：行程时间是5号到10号，那么保险时间应该是3号到12号）。</p></li></ul><p><br/></p>', '<ul class=\"dls list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"width: 678px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; padding: 10px 2px 2px 35px; margin: 0px 0px 0px 6px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(153, 153, 153); color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal; background: none rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span class=\"sp\">个人基本资料</span></ul><ul style=\"width: 678px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; padding: 12px 2px 10px 35px; margin: 3px 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal; background-image: url(http://www.tigerwing.cn/Content/images/line_01.gif); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-position: 50% 100%; background-repeat: repeat-x;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p><span class=\"vs_btn1\"></span></p></li><li><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(92, 92, 92); display: inline-block; margin: 0px; line-height: 14px;\">护照</strong></p></li><li><p style=\"line-height: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 480px;\">有效期需至少6个月或以上（从所申请签证有效期最后一天算起），护照至少有2页供使用的签证空白页，如有旧护照必须全部提供。（旧版护照尾页需持照人亲笔签名）。</p></li></ul><ul style=\"width: 678px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; padding: 12px 2px 10px 35px; margin: 3px 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal; background-image: url(http://www.tigerwing.cn/Content/images/line_01.gif); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-position: 50% 100%; background-repeat: repeat-x;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p><span class=\"vs_btn1\"></span></p></li><li><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(92, 92, 92); display: inline-block; margin: 0px; line-height: 14px;\">相片</strong></p></li><li><p style=\"line-height: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 480px;\">3张 近6个月内拍摄的白底两寸(3.5cm×4.5cm)相片。</p></li></ul><ul style=\"width: 678px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; padding: 12px 2px 10px 35px; margin: 3px 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal; background-image: url(http://www.tigerwing.cn/Content/images/line_01.gif); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-position: 50% 100%; background-repeat: repeat-x;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p><span class=\"vs_btn2\"></span></p></li><li><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(92, 92, 92); display: inline-block; margin: 0px; line-height: 14px;\">身份证</strong></p></li><li><p style=\"line-height: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 480px;\">请提供清晰的第二代身份证复印件（正反面需复印在同一页）。</p></li></ul><ul style=\"width: 678px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; padding: 12px 2px 10px 35px; margin: 3px 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal; background-image: url(http://www.tigerwing.cn/Content/images/line_01.gif); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-position: 50% 100%; background-repeat: repeat-x;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p><span class=\"vs_btn1\"></span></p></li><li><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(92, 92, 92); display: inline-block; margin: 0px; line-height: 14px;\">申根签证个人资料表</strong></p></li><li><p style=\"line-height: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 480px;\">请用认真填写每一项内容，字体清晰，该资料表的真实性及完整性，会直接影响签证结果。（请下载网站模板填写）</p></li></ul><ul style=\"width: 678px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; padding: 12px 2px 10px 35px; margin: 3px 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal; backgroun