 10px 35px; margin: 3px 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal; background-image: url(http://www.tigerwing.cn/Content/images/line_01.gif); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-position: 50% 100%; background-repeat: repeat-x;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p><span class=\"vs_btn1\"></span></p></li><li class=\"dtt\"><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(92, 92, 92); display: inline-block; margin: 0px; line-height: 14px;\">户口本</strong></p></li><li><p style=\"line-height: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 480px;\">请提供本人所在户口本上全体成员每一页的复印件；如果是集体户口，提供首页及本人页即可。</p></li></ul><ul style=\"width: 678px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; padding: 12px 2px 10px 35px; margin: 3px 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal; background-image: url(http://www.tigerwing.cn/Content/images/line_01.gif); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-position: 50% 100%; background-repeat: repeat-x;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p><span class=\"vs_btn1\"></span></p></li><li class=\"dtt\"><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(92, 92, 92); display: inline-block; margin: 0px; line-height: 14px;\">暂住证明资料</strong></p></li><li><p style=\"line-height: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 480px;\">1、申请人户口所在地或者护照签发地不属于该领区时，需提供该资料，签发需超过6个月；</p><p style=\"line-height: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 480px;\">2、如果没有暂住证/居住证，请提供派出所开具的暂住证明原件，显示居住时间需超过6个月。</p></li></ul><ul style=\"width: 678px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; padding: 12px 2px 10px 35px; margin: 3px 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal; background-image: url(http://www.tigerwing.cn/Content/images/line_01.gif); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-position: 50% 100%; background-repeat: repeat-x;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p><span class=\"vs_btn1\"></span></p></li><li class=\"dtt\"><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(92, 92, 92); display: inline-block; margin: 0px; line-height: 14px;\">结婚证明资料</strong></p></li><li><p style=\"line-height: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 480px;\">如已婚，请提供结婚证；如离异请提供离婚证复印件或法院调解书复印件。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"dls list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"width: 678px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; padding: 10px 2px 2px 35px; margin: 0px 0px 0px 6px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(153, 153, 153); color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal; background: none rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span class=\"sp\">中方单位资料</span></ul><ul style=\"width: 678px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; padding: 12px 2px 10px 35px; margin: 3px 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal; background-image: url(http://www.tigerwing.cn/Content/images/line_01.gif); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-position: 50% 100%; background-repeat: repeat-x;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p><span class=\"vs_btn1\"></span></p></li><li class=\"dtt\"><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(92, 92, 92); display: inline-block; margin: 0px; line-height: 14px;\">单位证明信</strong></p></li><li><p style=\"line-height: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 480px;\">请用工作单位正式信头纸打印，公司负责人签字并盖公章，并明确日期及如下信息: 任职公司的地址、电话和传真号码；公司签字人员的姓名和职务；申请人姓名、职务、收入和工作年限；行程目的；公司为申请人保留职位；费用承担方以及准假证明。（请参考网站模板）</p></li></ul><ul style=\"width: 678px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; padding: 12px 2px 10px 35px; margin: 3px 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal; background-image: url(http://www.tigerwing.cn/Content/images/line_01.gif); 